#### FormCard Wrapper Requirements

**⚠️ CRITICAL**: Each form section MUST be wrapped in a `FormCard` component with the `id` attribute and `title` prop.

**Props**:

- `id: string` - Required. Unique identifier for the form section (must match step IDs in multi-step forms)
- `title: string` - Required. Section title displayed in the card header
- `description?: string` - Optional. Description text displayed below the title
- `actions?: React.ReactNode` - Optional. Action buttons or elements displayed in the header (aligned to the right)
- `classNames?: { content?, header?, title?, wrapper?, description?, actions? }` - Optional. Custom CSS classes for styling specific parts of the card
- All `Card` component props are also accepted via spread operator

**Usage Examples**:

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - FormCard inside section component
// fields/basic-info.tsx
